<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>You've been invited to join Devv.me!</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8fafc; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
      .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
      .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
      .invitation-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f59e0b; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; }
      .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; }
      .cta-button:hover { background: #2563eb; }
      .cta-button.secondary { background: #10b981; }
      .cta-button.secondary:hover { background: #059669; }
      .profile-preview { background: #f1f5f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; }
      .profile-preview h3 { margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af; }
      .features { background: #f1f5f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .features ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; }
      .features li { margin: 8px 0; }
      .footer { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px 30px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b; }
      .unclaimed-notice { background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .unclaimed-notice strong { color: #92400e; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>🚀 You've been invited to Devv.me!</h1>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9;">Your professional developer profile is ready</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <div class="invitation-badge">🎯 Personal Invitation</div>
        
        <h2>Hi <%= @user.display_name %>!</h2>
        
        <p><%= @admin_name %> has created a professional developer profile for you on Devv.me. Your profile is already live and ready to be claimed!</p>
        
        <div class="profile-preview">
          <h3>📋 Your Profile Preview</h3>
          <p><strong>Username:</strong> @<%= @user.username %></p>
          <p><strong>Profile URL:</strong> <a href="<%= @profile_url %>" style="color: #3b82f6;"><%= @profile_url %></a></p>
          <% if @user.job_title.present? %>
            <p><strong>Role:</strong> <%= @user.job_title %></p>
          <% end %>
          <% if @user.location.present? %>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= @user.location %></p>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="unclaimed-notice">
          <strong>⚠️ Profile Status:</strong> Your profile is currently marked as "unclaimed" but is publicly visible. Claim it to take full control and start adding your projects and content!
        </div>
        
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="<%= @claim_url %>" class="cta-button">🔐 Claim Your Profile</a>
        </p>
        
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px;">
          <a href="<%= @profile_url %>" class="cta-button secondary">👀 Preview Your Profile</a>
        </p>
        
        <p>Once you claim your profile, you'll be able to:</p>
        
        <div class="features">
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Take full control</strong> of your profile and make updates</li>
            <li><strong>Add your projects</strong> with rich descriptions and images</li>
            <li><strong>Write and publish blog posts</strong> with our markdown editor</li>
            <li><strong>Connect your social profiles</strong> and showcase your work</li>
            <li><strong>Set your password</strong> and access your dashboard</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>Important:</strong> This invitation link will expire in 30 days. Make sure to claim your profile before then!</p>
        
        <p>Welcome to the Devv.me community!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br><%= @admin_name %><br>Devv.me Team</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>You're receiving this email because <%= @admin_name %> created a profile for you on Devv.me.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@devv.me" style="color: #3b82f6;">support@devv.me</a></p>
        <p>This invitation expires on <%= (@user.invitation_sent_at + 30.days).strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
